data.description: Welcome to this sun–filled three bedroom, two full and one half bathroom home in Cobblestone. The welcoming front living room boasts a soaring two-story vaulted ceiling with skylights and the spacious dining room can accommodate any size gathering. Kick your feet up and relax in the family room with a cozy wood-burning fireplace. The eat-in kitchen highlights granite counters, a pantry, and a breakfast area with sliding glass doors outside. A half bathroom and access to the garage finish the main level. Upstairs, the primary bedroom suite features two-walk-in closets and a private bathroom with a soaking tub and walk-in shower. Another two bedrooms and a second full bathroom complete the upper level. Downstairs, the lower level awaits your finishing touches to meet your needs. Enjoy spending time outside in the fully-fenced backyard with a large deck. Fantastic location right off Reisterstown Road with quick access to 695, 795 and a wide variety of excellent restaurants, shopping, entertainment options and more. Some photos have been virtually staged. Sold as-is. Taking back up offers
